uk.ac.aber.dcs.slj11.wordplay.datastruct.graph
Class Node<Key>

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.aber.dcs.slj11.wordplay.datastruct.graph.Node<Key>

public class Node<Key>
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a single node (vertex) in the graph. Holds data about the particular vertex and holds a list of neighbour nodes.

Author:
Samuel Jackson (slj11@aber.ac.uk)
